==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Postentry
<hw>Post"en*try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>entry</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A second or
subsequent, at the customhouse, of goods which had been omitted by
mistake.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bookkeeping)</fld> <def>An additional or subsequent
entry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Poster</ent>⟦br⟧
